algorithms.trees

Class TDP_Eager

  • java.lang.Object
    • algorithms.trees.TDP_Anyk_Iterator
      • algorithms.trees.TDP_Part
        • algorithms.trees.TDP_Eager

  • public class TDP_Eager
extends TDP_Part
    Eager is a variant of Anyk-Part that implements get_successors(entities.trees.TDP_Decision) by sorting the decision set eagerly (upon the first visit with initialize_partial_order(entities.trees.TDP_DecisionSet)). After sorting is complete, each decision points to its exact successor.
    Author:
    Nikolaos Tziavelis
